SUMMARY:The Green Party
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:Green Party is a split bill show from two of London’s best up
  and coming comedians (and great pals)\, Nick Morey and Indi Madray. Nick i
 s an early 40’s gay man with a love of video games\, wordplay\, and a hos
 t of embarrassing\, self-deprecating tales. In just two years on the comedy
  scene\, he’s proven himself as one to watch\, with deft wordplay\, surpr
 ising voice work\, and a mastery of the misdirect. A walking cultural ident
 ity crisis\, Indi shares her experiences\, deconstructing stereo-typical ex
 pectations. An Award winning comedian\, Indi's a regular on the Comedy Circ
 uit earning numerous bragging rights and accolades in her nine years on the
  circuit. A ‘joint’ venture\, these two have bonded over the lighter th
 ings in life\, dreaming of a world where the grass is always greener. Come 
 hang\, it’ll be fun!\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/eve
 nt/the-green-party/
URL:https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/the-green-party/
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
